@UserManagementAPI_HostAddress = https://localhost:7133
@ApiToken = techhive-api-key-2026

### GET /users – Lista todos os usuários (esperado: 200)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

###

### GET /users – Sem token (esperado: 401)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users
Accept: application/json

###

### GET /users – Token inválido (esperado: 401)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer token-invalido

###

### GET /users/{id} – Retorna um usuário específico por ID (esperado: 200)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

###

### GET /users/{id} – Usuário inexistente (esperado: 404)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/99999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

###

### POST /users – Cria um novo usuário (esperado: 201)
POST {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

{
  "fullName": "João Paulo Souza",
  "email": "joao.souza@techhive.com",
  "department": "TI",
  "role": "Desenvolvedor Full Stack",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### POST /users – Payload inválido (esperado: 400)
POST {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

{
  "fullName": " ",
  "email": "email-invalido",
  "department": "T",
  "role": "",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### PUT /users/{id} – Atualiza os dados de um usuário existente (esperado: 200)
PUT {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Ana Beatriz Ramos",
  "email": "ana.ramos@techhive.com",
  "department": "RH",
  "role": "Gerente de Recursos Humanos",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### PUT /users/{id} – Payload inválido (esperado: 400)
PUT {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

{
  "fullName": "",
  "email": "nao-e-email",
  "department": "",
  "role": "",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### PUT /users/{id} – Usuário inexistente (esperado: 404)
PUT {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Usuario Inexistente",
  "email": "inexistente@techhive.com",
  "department": "TI",
  "role": "Analista",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### DELETE /users/{id} – Remove um usuário pelo ID (esperado: 204)
DELETE {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/11
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

###

### DELETE /users/{id} – Usuário inexistente (esperado: 404)
DELETE {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{ApiToken}}

###
